<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.5">
<l>vilaṅkum kayalum vēlumoṇ kāviyum veṇṟakaṇ</l>
<l>calamkoṇ ṭacollār tāṅkaḷci rittika ḻātamuṉ</l>
<l>malaṅkum varālum vāḷaiyum pāyvayal cūḻtaru</l>
<l>nalaṅkoḷ naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tumeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before those whose words bear anger can scold, tittering,</l>
<l>With eyes that surpass does, kayal [fish], spears, and bright lilies,</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in prosperity-filled Naṟaiyūr</l>
<l>Whose fields encircle [it] effortlessly where leap wriggly varāl and vāḷai [fish].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
